{"id": "1448642473441099776", "channel_id": "1440250898688508016", "type": 19, "author_id": "1001696859225591869", "author_name": "o5214658", "author_bot": false, "content": "兩個方法都已嘗試，單獨使用與合併使用皆已嘗試，結果相同：依舊是跑完廠商圖標後黑屏。\n安裝位置直接於C：\\\n經過圖片對比，新安裝好的程式中缺少這個dll（如圖標記）。", "timestamp": "2025-12-11T11:48:00.144000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1448642473185382491", "filename": "image-12.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 306682, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1440250898688508016/1448642473185382491/image-12.jpg?ex=69cbb470&is=69ca62f0&hm=b7ffc831ed1642e91676052ead7b403cd2746d03bddfbf3f241514b1c7d8327f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1448585562624884786", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1440250898688508016", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」繁中PC端黑屏", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168197425172480"]}
